pageInformationsDescription.en:
This is a draft self-assessment questionnaire for your professional competences as VET teacher and/or trainer.

The questionnaire covers a number of competence areas relevant for your professional success.

  1. VET curriculum design;
  2. Organisation of the teaching and training process;
  3. VET didactics;
  4. Formative assessment of learning.

 

This questionnaire will help you to identify areas of proficiency and such, in which additional learning may be beneficial for you. It serves as entry test, based on which you can select learning modules for further self-study.

The following statements relate to the competence areas and are ranked in a progressive order (from basic to high competence level). Choose the statement which expresses best what you feel is right.
